What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Microwave Oven Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Microwave Oven Market

The microwave oven market is expected to witness market growth at a rate of 3.5% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on microwave oven market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecast period while providing their impacts on the market’s growth. The rise in standard of living of customers globally is escalating the growth of microwave oven market.

Microwave ovens refer to the electronic devices which make use of the utilize electromagnetic waves to cook and heat food and beverage products in a shorter duration of time. The electromagnetic waves or microwaves tend to radiate heat in the form of microwave energy. This energy is further exposed to the water molecules present in food products.

The rise in the number of working population and their preoccupied schedules of people in urban cities acts as the major factors driving the growth of microwave oven market. The increase in number of nuclear families, high demand for frozen and ready-to-eat food and growth of sales of smart kitchen appliances accelerate the microwave oven market growth. The expansion of hospitality sector and increasing catering contracts for large-scale functions, seminars and other social gatherings and rise in the adoption of kitchen and home appliances because of increasing rate of urbanization further influence the microwave oven market. Additionally, rising standard of living of customers, growth in population, rise in awareness about different cooking appliances, increase in consumer spending on kitchen appliances and surge in disposable income of consumers positively affect the microwave oven market. Furthermore, rise in trend of connectivity between home appliances and innovations such as inverter-based microwave oven extend profitable opportunities to the microwave oven market players in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

On the other hand, high power consumption associated with the usage of these products is expected to obstruct the microwave oven market growth. The rise in concerns regarding energy conservation across the globe is projected to challenge the microwave oven market in the forecast period of 2021-2028.

